IRS990ScheduleA.FactsAndCircumstancesTest: THE SUPREME COUNCIL BENEVOLENT FOUNDATION QUALIFIES AS A PUBLICLY SUPPORTED ORGANIZATION UNDER THE FACTS AND CIRCUMSTANCES TESTS. THE PUBLIC SUPPORT PERCENTAGE IS GREATER THAN 10%. THE ORGANIZATION IS STRUCTURED AND OPERATED IN SUCH MANNER AS TO ATTRACT PUBLIC SUPPORT ON A CONTINUAL BASIS. THE ENDOWMENT INCOME IS GENERATED FROM AN ENDOWMENT ORGINALLY FUNDED BY PUBLIC SUPPORT. CONTRIBUTIONS ARE RECEIVED FROM A LARGE NUMBER OF DONORS. THE GOVERNING BODY REPRESENTS THE INTERESTS OF THE ENTIRE MEMBERSHIP. THE BENEVOLENT FOUNDATION SERVICES ARE PROVIDED FREE OF CHARGE TO THE RECIPIENTS.
